<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
        <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting" />
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
        <title>BuckHill</title>
        <style>
            table, td, div, h1, p {
                font-family: "Nunito", sans-serif;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body style="margin: 0; padding-left: 15%;padding-right: 15%; padding-top: 10%">
        <img
            src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhdeyv7ba/image/upload/v1712400955/image-20230724-084138_jebbtg_rk0ctg.png"
            alt="email_logo"
            style="
                    height: auto;
                    width: 100%;
                    display: block;
                    object-fit: contain;
                "
        />
          <span
            style="display: block;padding: 0 10px;margin: 0 auto;">
            <p style="font-size: 15px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 20px; margin: 20px 0 20px;color: black;" >
                Dear
                {{firstname}}
                {{lastname}},<br/>
                {{middlename}} We are contacting you because there
                is an <i>amount due</i> on your purchase <br/>
                {{purchase_id}}:
            </p>
        </span>
        <table
        align="center"
        style="border-bottom-right-radius: 10px; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px; border: solid 1px transparent; padding: 10px; border-collapse: collapse; width: 85%;"
        >
            <caption
                style="
                        background: #281f52;
                        color: #ffffff;
                        border-top-right-radius: 10px;
                        border-top-left-radius: 10px;
                        padding: 5px;
                        font-size: 16px;
                        font-weight: 700;
                    "
            >
                Purchase Summary
            </caption>
            <tr style="border-bottom: solid 1px #9e9e9e">
                <td style="padding: 14px 10px">Date:</td>
                <td>{{purchase_date}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{#each purchases}}
                <tr style="background: #ebebeb; border-bottom: solid 1.5px #d2d2d2;" >
                    <td style="padding: 14px 10px">{{this.quantity}}x</td>
                    <td>{{this.name}}</td>
                    <td>{{this.price}}</td>
                </tr>
            {{/each}}
                <tr>
                    <td></td>
                    <td style="padding: 14px 0px">
                        <strong>Total Amount</strong>
                    </td>
                    <td>{{total_amount}} <b>Kn</b></td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background: #ebebeb; border: solid 1px transparent" >
                    <td></td>
                    <td style="padding: 14px 0px">
                        <strong>Amount Paid</strong>
                    </td>
                    <td>{{amount_paid}} <b>Kn</b></td>
                </tr>
        </table>
        <p style=" margin: 40px 0 40px;font-weight:600; font-size: 15px; color: black; " >
            According to our records, the <i>amount due</i> is
            {{amount_due}}
            Kn. Please, click on the next button
            <b>to pay</b>
            this difference:
        </p>
        <a
            href="https://pet-shop.buckhill.com.hr/checkout",
            target="_blank"
            style="
                    text-decoration: none;
                    color: #ffffff;
                    padding: 8px 17px;
                    background: #281f52;
                    border-radius: 50px;
                    text-align: center;
                    font-size: 16px;
                    font-weight: 700;
                    border: none;
                    outline: none;
                    display: block;
                    width: 177px;
                    margin: 40px auto;
                "
        >
            PAY NOW
        </a>
        <p style=" margin: 40px 0 40px;font-weight:600; font-size: 15px; color: black; " >
                If you have any other concerns, please contact our technical support team.
                <br /><br />
                Kind regards,
                <br /><br />
                Petson Team
                <br /><br />
                <br /><br />
        </p>

    </body>
</html>